AN ENERGY-EFFICIENT COMPRESSIVE SENSING FRAMEWORK INCORPORATING
ONLINE DICTIONARY LEARNING FOR LONG-TERM WIRELESS HEALTH MONITORING
Kai XU, Yixing Li, Fengbo Ren

